Hands-On Task

Implement a Media Player Command System with the following setup:

Task Objective:
    Create a media player controller that can:
        Play music
        Pause music
        Stop music
    Your system must contain:
        Command interface with execute()
        3 concrete commands: PlayCommand, PauseCommand, StopCommand
        MediaPlayer as the Receiver
        RemoteControl as the Invoker
        Main to simulate client setup and execution

Expected Output:
    Music is playing...
    Music paused.
    Music stopped.